latestIgtvVideos.title: HAPPY INTERNATIONAL DANCE DAY
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Dance isn't just dance
it's magical!!
Something that sets you free 💃

Watch me dancing to the tunes of 'Mera Piya Ghar aaya'...some three years ago.
Actually I had planned and practiced on this for performing on my mehendi night just a day before my marriage in November 1996. Yes that was a pre cellphone era. I could not perform that night as my husband did not turn up for the event 🤪 . (Oh.. I am yet to settle that score🤔🤣)
Though ours is a dance loving family..yet did not get to perform on this number until this day that happened almost after 22 years of our wedding 😅

Happy International Dance Day everyone! ...enjoyyy!!
